  }, "Data Ingestion and Transformation"), mdx("p", null, "The primary step for collecting your data for analytics is to ingest it from all your sources including your in-house applications, SaaS tools, data from your IoT devices, and all other sources. Various tools are available to make this process a seamless experience. "), mdx("h4", {
